subtitleNullable: First frame of all deepfake videos resize to 512x512
descriptionNullable:
This dataset is all of the first frames from the deepfake competition resized to 512x512 in order to make more accessible to more people. This is accompanied by a train_df file which captures all of the labels and also the original videos the fakes came from. this can be easily used to make a simple image classification approach to deepfake detection. 

This data was created by iterating through the videos and utilizes Dieters resize to square found here https://www.kaggle.com/christofhenkel/extract-image-features-from-pretrained-nn
